    {
      "_id": "n7PA3IqGBt8rBX3w",
      "name": "Engulf",
      "type": "feat",
      "img": "icons/svg/aura.svg",
      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>The cube moves up to its Speed without provoking Opportunity Attacks. The cube can move through the spaces of Large or smaller creatures if it has room inside itself to contain them (see the Ooze Cube trait). Teste de Resistência de Destreza: CD 12, cada criatura whose space the cube enters for the first time during this move. 10 (3d6) dano de ácido, and o alvo is engulfed. An engulfed target is suffocating, can't cast spells with a Verbal component, fica com a condição Impedido, and takes 10 (3d6) dano de ácido at the start of each of the cube's turns. When the cube moves, the engulfed target moves with it. An engulfed target can try to escape by taking an action to make a CD 12 Força (Athletics) check. On a successful check, o alvo escapes and enters the nearest unoccupied space. Metade do dano, and o alvo moves to an unoccupied space within 1,5 m of the cube. If there is no unoccupied space, o alvo fails the save instead.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
